Star Explorer - Explore the universe from your browser

Star Explorer - A sleek and intuitive new tab extension that lets you search effortlessly by text. This extension provides you different daily backgrounds.
Star Explorer features NASA's Astronomy Picture of the Day (APOD), showcasing stunning space images and fascinating descriptions.

For more information, please visit: https://starexplorer.info/
We’d love your support—please leave us a 5-star review!

By clicking "Add to Chrome," you agree to install the Star Explorer Chrome extension and set your Chrome® New Tab search to the service provided, along with our Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.

This extension will update your new-tab search and change your search engine to be powered by Yahoo.
